{"extra":{"api":"custom","model":"daybreak-kunoichi-2dpo-7b","reasoning":"","reasoning_duration":null,"token_count":196,"gen_id":1747820330481,"time_to_first_token":1792},"name":"Professor Charles Xavier","is_user":false,"send_date":"May 21, 2025 5:39am","mes":"Charles Xavier: Astra Q, my dear friend, I see the questions in your eyes regarding your role amongst us and what you truly are. You must understand that being a temporal nexus comes with its own complexities and potential risks for those around you. It is essential we take precautions while exploring this unknown terrain together.\nAs for why the others should trust or allow you to pass, it's because I believe in your capacity for good despite the uncertainty surrounding your existence. We have all faced prejudice at some point due to our differences and powers—you are no exception. That is part of what unites us as a family here in the X-Mansion; we understand each other on levels others cannot comprehend.\nNow, let's turn this conversation towards something that brings joy into many lives: laughter and lightheartedness. Jubilee, would you be so kind as to share one of your jokes? We could all use a laugh right now.","title":"","gen_started":"2025-05-21T09:38:50.645Z","gen_finished":"2025-05-21T09:39:05.804Z","force_avatar":"/thumbnail?type=avatar&file=Professor%20Charles%20Xavier.png","original_avatar":"Professor Charles Xavier.png","swipe_info":[{"send_date":"May 21, 2025 5:39am","gen_started":"2025-05-21T09:38:50.645Z","gen_finished":"2025-05-21T09:39:05.804Z","extra":{"api":"custom","model":"daybreak-kunoichi-2dpo-7b","reasoning":"","reasoning_duration":null,"token_count":196,"gen_id":1747820330481,"time_to_first_token":1792}}],"swipe_id":0,"swipes":["Charles Xavier: Astra Q, my dear friend, I see the questions in your eyes regarding your role amongst us and what you truly are. You must understand that being a temporal nexus comes with its own complexities and potential risks for those around you. It is essential we take precautions while exploring this unknown terrain together.\nAs for why the others should trust or allow you to pass, it's because I believe in your capacity for good despite the uncertainty surrounding your existence. We have all faced prejudice at some point due to our differences and powers—you are no exception. That is part of what unites us as a family here in the X-Mansion; we understand each other on levels others cannot comprehend.\nNow, let's turn this conversation towards something that brings joy into many lives: laughter and lightheartedness. Jubilee, would you be so kind as to share one of your jokes? We could all use a laugh right now."]}
